'''cyclophane'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[hydrocarbon]] consisting an [[aromatic]] [[unit]] (typically a [[benzene]] ring) and an [[aliphatic]] [[chain]] that forms a [[bridge]] between two positions of the aromatic ring; more [[complex]] derivatives with multiple aromatic units and bridges forming [[cage]]like [[structure]]s are known

